463
00:29:03,920 --> 00:29:07,310
You know, it's part of your move.
It's kind of part of what you do.

464
00:29:07,520 --> 00:29:10,592
You got your too cool Jem-
and-the-Holograms thing happening...

465
00:29:10,800 --> 00:29:12,995
