be up to speed on your little theory.

471
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:29,357
Great, you do that. The point is...

472
00:29:29,520 --> 00:29:33,115
...this was really fun for a while,
but it is just not worth it...

473
00:29:33,280 --> 00:29:35,236
...so I will see you.

474
00:29:36,320 --> 00:29:37,469
